朋友身體力行過大海支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3740722244c6cd12764067907402e66753aae709","tid":1380184,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:12:38.000Z","msg":"好恐怖"},{"pid":"d4c94d6aa965c3cb8a4e767aa59c45936621605f","tid":1380184,"uid":72647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:13:40.000Z","msg":"聽聞佢地自己同入境處人員講去示威。<br />\n試問邊個會俾一個黎示威既遊客入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話去上環買海味咪得囉"},{"pid":"7063454fa71afb8ca99af4ad35e42182e131cbbd","tid":1380184,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:14:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Hong Kong is</span></span> <del>not</del> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">China</span></span><del>, not yet!</del>"},{"pid":"845a7fd97c6a7597ad6d50b5ac7f36eaedb4d266","tid":1380184,"uid":102609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50023761b6a21a0b93705c1138edbd183f5471e3","tid":1380184,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:12:01.000Z","msg":"橙報，保持距離"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:16:37.000Z","msg":"啱啱查過<br />\n橙報同橙新聞唔同<br />\n澳門大學學生會傳播學會旗下學生媒體。每兩個月在校內外出版月刊，內容分時事版與校園版。<br />\n澳門大學學生會唔知有冇染到紅<br />\n但係見澳門論盡媒體（親泛民）都轉載呢單新聞<br />\n所以應該可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5636cdbb2e4e7cb4b715d5b846b165e30c738222","tid":1380184,"uid":260759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:18:14.000Z","msg":"咁樣其實係咪間接鎖國<br />\n唔比出入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f10a9bf79108b43bf85ed272d0d29c924c1945","tid":1380184,"uid":24750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5636cdbb2e4e7cb4b715d5b846b165e30c738222","tid":1380184,"uid":260759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:18:14.000Z","msg":"咁樣其實係咪間